# Cline AI Rules - Kancelaria Adwokacka Website

## Project Type
Professional law office website - HTML/CSS/JavaScript with Bootstrap 5.3.2

## Technology Constraints
- ✅ HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript ES6+
- ✅ Bootstrap 5.3.2, Font Awesome 6.5.1
- ✅ Vite build system
- ❌ NO TypeScript, React, Vue, Angular

## Critical Requirements
1. RODO/GDPR compliance in all forms
2. WCAG 2.1 Level AA accessibility
3. Mobile-first responsive design
4. Professional Polish language
5. SEO for "adwokat Trzebnica", legal services

## Code Style
- HTML: Semantic elements, Bootstrap components
- CSS: Mobile-first, BEM naming, CSS variables
- JS: ES6+, no jQuery, async/await, error handling

## Must Include in Forms
```html
<input type="checkbox" required>
<label>Zgoda na przetwarzanie danych osobowych zgodnie z RODO</label>
```

## Testing
```bash
npm run lint     # Before committing
npm test         # Including a11y tests
npm run format   # Auto-format code
```

## Documentation
Read: AGENTS.md, docs/RODO.md, docs/SEO.md

